article.headline: (5) STANFORD 91, EASTERN WASH 50
article.story:
ANCHORAGE, Alaska (Ticker) -- Candice Wiggins scored 18 points 
and Brooke Smith added 17 as fifth-ranked Stanford beat Eastern
Washington, 91-50, in the semifinals of the Great Alaska
Shootout.

The Cardinal will play Louisiana-Lafayette in the finals on
Wednesday.

Stanford (3-0) closed the first half on an 11-0 run to lead
44-22 at the half and scored the first 12 points of the second
half.

Felice Moore scored 11 points for Eastern Washington (0-2).
